questions.quote: Hey Jerry don't worry about it all right. The important thing is, is we got to catch up. Mind if I ah, grab the want ads?
Ah, back to normal. Not bad for four thousand bucks. . . . I can't believe I got the Low Fat!
I'd really like to go, Elaine. But, George is coming back from the hospital. I gotta wait for him. But otherwise I would definitely go.
Well, I'll see you guys later.  Nice meeting you. Bye Elaine.
So, dad, lemme ask you a question. How many people work at these big law offices?
Another productive meeting. By the way, I saw that English Patient film last night. It was extraordinary.
Hey, Braun, I got good news and bad news. And they're both the same: you're fired. Costanza, you've won the water pik!
She's on the lease! George you have got to find another place for me.
Jerry, can't you just give it one more day, it's not his fault.
Ha ha ha ha. Yeah, well, I'll tell you, she's a full-figured gal.
